items.title: Better than Gym
items.text: I have went to gym for two months and didn't see much of a desired result. With better me, only keeping aside 20 mins a day for 28-30 days made me feel more confident with the results
items.name: Rishad

items.title: Loving this app
items.text: I had never done much calisthenics. I used to lift a lot as a younger man. Decided to try calisthenics. Amazing. I am getting great workouts and also having much less back issues.
items.name: Theodore

items.title: Very easy to follow
items.text: The length of the workouts are perfect for a beginner or a returner. The videos are a good pace and make it foolproof for the easily distracted. The timer function helps keep you on track and when you’ll get to move to the next thing.
